<p>2.安装需要的版本：</p>

{% highlight %}
{% highlight %}docker pull secfa/awvs{% endhighlight %}

{% highlight %}Using default tag: latest
latest: Pulling from secfa/awvs
c60272505ec1: Pull complete
1b433e541802: Pull complete
Digest: sha256:3e3c8146358a9e6d5865732bf447cd1d5850001e53465d04df14afd606789684
Status: Downloaded newer image for secfa/awvs:latest{% endhighlight %}

<p>3.查看镜像</p>

{% highlight %}
{% highlight %}docker images{% endhighlight %}

<p>或者仅查看awvs镜像：</p>

{% highlight %}
{% highlight %}docker images | grep awvs

secfa/awvs&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; latest&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 58b159caafe9&nbsp;&nbsp; 5 weeks ago&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1.22GB{% endhighlight %}

<p>4.启动awvs</p>

{% highlight %}
{% highlight %}docker run -itd -p 9999:3443 --cap-add LINUX_IMMUTABLE --name my-awvs secfa/awvs

9fe2356f8547f8655f3c94ae84771e33c402133c0a8d81c88037b8dfa524ded4{% endhighlight %}

<p>然后在浏览器访问：https://localhost:9999/ 即可登录</p>

<p><img src="data:image/png;base64," style="height:389px; width:306px" /></p>

<p>（第一次登录不知道邮箱和密码可以进入docker进行重置）</p>

<p><img src="data:image/png;base64," /></p>

<p>5.进入镜像修改登录密码：</p>

{% highlight %}
{% highlight %}sudo docker ps -a | grep awvs
9fe2356f8547   secfa/awvs                     &quot;/bin/sh /awvs_start&hellip;&quot;   13 minutes ago   Up 13 minutes                0.0.0.0:9999-&gt;3443/tcp, :::9999-&gt;3443/tcp                                            my-awvs
linlin@linlin-i5:/etc/mysql$ docker exec -it 9fe2356f8547 bash{% endhighlight %}

<p>进入目录：</p>

{% highlight %}
{% highlight %}cd /home/acunetix/.acunetix{% endhighlight %}

<p>执行修改密码的文件</p>

{% highlight %}
{% highlight %}./change_credentials.sh{% endhighlight %}

<p>设置邮箱和密码：（例如 admin@email.com&nbsp; <span style="background-color:#f7f7f7; color:#000000; font-family:-apple-system,system-ui,BlinkMacSystemFont,&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,Roboto,Oxygen-Sans,Ubuntu,Cantarell,&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,sans-serif; font-size:18px">MyPassword!123</span>）</p>
